Today 2,400 7-day average</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5r56txk</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[evaunit117]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Designed a bit of a daring dress for V-Day!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CuXwEdo</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XUEV9FN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Does this look deceptively simple? Yeah, I guess it does a bit. This was a little bit of a challenge to myself to work my patternmatching skills. I drafted this pattern using my bodice block. The bodice pattern just has 3 pieces—the neckline, the side front and the side back! The skirt is 4x quarter circle pieces to create those sweet chevrons.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4rxHZzF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The amazing thing about the bodice is that the neckline pattern piece is one straight, simple piece that goes from front to back (mirrored on both sides and matched down the middle). So there is no shoulder seam! The challenge here was preventing it from gaping and connecting the two sides at an angle that wasn’t too far off the shoulders and not cut too low in the front or the back. Geometry gone wild, y’all.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Cfr6ztI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The back v is low but sits just above my bra which I’m really happy about because I’ve never been a fan of designs where you have to be braless for it to work. The invisible zipper was super challenging to match stripes on both sides. I kind of wish I painted the pull red with a little nail polish but it’s fine for now. My secret to a good zipper? Fusible hem tape to act as interfacing. Interfacing sucks and the hem tape works SO much better, my god.

Anyways, I hemmed the skirt with a bias tape facing (AFTER trimming a few days after hanging it). Always gotta hang your bias skirts before hemming, don’t skip that.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/76i9cDO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The neckline on the front is pretty daring for me but I’m glad the design didn’t force it to be even lower than that! I think on the next iteration if I make this again, I will pull up the shoulders about a centimetre to firm up the neckline a little. We’re all learning as we go, nothing is ever as perfect as it might look!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/N7S8YM7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>As you can see a bit better from this picture, the skirt is made up of 4 pieces and is pattern matched along the front, back, and even the side seams. I just love the chevrons! Definitely planning a rainbow pride dress using this pattern one day when I can afford 5 more metres of cotton drill fabric.

I sewed this over just about 4 livestreams, including the test run! I stream my work 4 times per week, a lot of patternmaking and some cross stitch and miscellaneous stuff thrown in.

If you wanna watch me sewing stuff live, here is a shameless plug: http://twitch.tv/carbonchic</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CuXwEdo</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CarbonChic]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>How was your Valentine’s Day?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/S2spqdE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4MYxuY0.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>HappyValentine’sDay</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/S2spqdE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Goofychems]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Funny Random Meme and Twitter Dump</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/obuFJU0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6es40nu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uN0VPAD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/z4N3L9n.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HIrI0i5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h2ZYsRA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cWurpkP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZieJLZQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e8Ctlyi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FGhp9j6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MSCqt3T.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/