TLDR warning: if you don't want to read the story, jus read the memes.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Y9q3PRA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Ok, so. Hotel room reserved, car topped up for oil change & fresh tires, & he had taken 2 days off work so we could spend the weekend together! WOO!

... except... as soon as he got here, his face was buried in his phone all thru our first dinner... 

This does not bode well.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3AR3Cjm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It started bad, & just went downhill from there. First night at the hotel, he wasn't even remotely interested, & was far more interested in watching TV until 10pm, then playing video games until 1am, before heading to bed.

"Ok, he just drove a long journey, there's always Sunday!"

... and then....</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1Kp3ZJu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Once. A single time for the whole 4-day weekend. Not even heavy petting the rest of the time. Just... a single encounter for the whole weekend, & he was back to his TV & video games.

Really says something about my sex life that the highlight of the whole weekend was watching the Halftime Show...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LYFnmyz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And then he drops this little factoid in my lap right before we were set to leave the hotel.

So, I take time off work for the weekend, take the time & energy to shave my legs (bc, ladies, let's be honest: in the winter in cold areas, no one bothers to shave your legs unless you have a legit reason/excuse), & pack all the cute clothes for dates & whatnot...

And then it turns out I was being used to help him cheat on his partner.

If it wasn't for the fact I'm so thoroughly disappointed in his performance/visit, I might actually be mad.

Now, to look up his partner & decide if I want to tell them where he really was this weekend. Bc he allegedly told them he was going somewhere else.

See, this is why so many of us have trust issues. That & oatmeal raisin cookies.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZHJeiMO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cat tax. Yes, his collar edge is left long on purpose. It's a Sentry Comfort Collar, & he yanks it off if you cut the tail off. So I leave it long, just to keep him from getting irritated & pulling it off.

TLDR: just read the memes, like I said at the top.

MV edit: Well, so glad to know that my disgustingly depressing sex life is entertaining. I would like to personally thank the guys who have made sure I got this far, but CBA. 

Be excellent to each other, folks. And quit wasting time on guys with more dick in their personality than in their pants.

MV edit part 2: Look, I keep getting so much flack for my oatmeal raisin cookie comment. I ain't got a problem with oatmeal. Or raisins. I just don't like cooked raisins. & I especially don't like biting into a cooked raisin, after being told it was chocolate.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/TQicviI</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SerenePrincess013]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I'll get the egg next time, now I'll have my drink</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KhPQ07r</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nMkvjRy.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KhPQ07r</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[cyan1618]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>That's meth'd up</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/U7sKrFA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/727pBwd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/U7sKrFA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[RoRoBeans]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Self-victimization</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qgkO6Mq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XjRVLUg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qgkO6Mq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mugjunk]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Nothing To See Here, Move Along...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/P17a2vw</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/80ZqN0a.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Past is Prologue</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/P17a2vw</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Nexus297]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I know what you just did</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/TXvnlag</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Kh